## Abstract-Specific Patterns

### Chain Configuration
- Always use environment-aware chain selection (abstract vs abstractTestnet)
- Extend viem clients with `eip712WalletActions()` for ZKsync compatibility:
```ts
const walletClient = createWalletClient({
  chain: abstract,
  transport: custom(window.ethereum),
}).extend(eip712WalletActions())
```
